@startuml
autonumber

actor "小明" as Ming
participant "Scanner" as Scan
participant "BorrowingSystem" as Sys
participant "User" as U

Note over Ming, U: Use Case: 登入 (Login)

Ming -> Scan : 插入借書卡
activate Scan
Scan -> Scan : scanCard()
Scan -> Sys : 傳送卡號 (userId)
deactivate Scan

activate Sys
Sys -> U : login(password/id)
activate U
' 這裡假設驗證邏輯在 User 或 System 都可以，通常查資料庫
U --> Sys : true (驗證成功)
deactivate U

alt 登入成功
    Sys --> Ming : 顯示歡迎畫面
else 登入失敗
    Sys --> Ming : 顯示錯誤與重試
end

deactivate Sys
@enduml
